-cambridge-14-test-2-part-1-2023-01-29-21-15-54/27.mp3","time_start":74.13,"time_end":75.61},{"position":28,"content":"That's good to hear.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-14-test-2-part-1-2023-01-29-21-15-54/28.mp3","time_start":75.66,"time_end":77.05},{"position":29,"content":"Right, so one more thing I need to know before we talk about why you're here, Julie,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-14-test-2-part-1-2023-01-29-21-15-54/29.mp3","time_start":77.22,"time_end":81.34},{"position":30,"content":"and that's the name of your insurance company.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-14-test-2-part-1-2023-01-29-21-15-54/30.mp3","time_start":81.45,"time_end":83.74},{"position":31,"content":"It's Cawley Life Insurance,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-14-test-2-part-1-2023-01-29-21-15-54/31.mp3","time_start":83.89,"time_end":85.85},{"position":32,"content":"that's CAWLEY.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-14-test-2-part-1-2023-01-29-21-15-54/32.mp3","time_start":85.85,"time_end":89.71},{"position":33,"content":"Excellent, thank you so much.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-14-test-2-part-1-2023-01-29-21-15-54/33.mp3","time_start":89.79,"time_end":91.95},{"position":34,"content":"Now Julie, let's look at how we can help you.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-14-test-2-part-1-2023-01-29-21-15-54/34.mp3","time_start":92.56,"time_end":95.36},{"position":35,"content":"So tell me a little about what brought you here today.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-14-test-2-part-1-2023-01-29-21-15-54/35.mp3","time_start":95.46,"time_end":98.01},{"position":36,"content":"Well, I've been getting a pain in my knee, the left one.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-14-test-2-part-1-2023-01-29-21-15-54/36.mp3","time_start":98.01,"time_end":102.13},{"position":37,"content":"Not very serious at first, but it's gotten worse,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-14-test-2-part-1-2023-01-29-21-15-54/37.mp3","time_start":102.27,"time_end":105.74},{"position":38,"content":"so I thought I ought to see someone about it.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-14-test-2-part-1-2023-01-29-21-15-54/38.mp3","time_start":105.74,"time_end":108.27},{"position":39,"content":"That's certainly the right decision.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-14-test-2-part-1-2023-01-29-21-15-54/39.mp3","time_start":108.27,"time_end":109.85},{"position":40,"content":"So how long have you been aware of this pain?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-14-test-2-part-1-2023-01-29-21-15-54/40.mp3","time_start":110.09,"time_end":112.13},{"position":41,"content":"Is it just a few days, or is it longer than that?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-14-test-2-part-1-2023-01-29-21-15-54/41.mp3","time_start":112.13,"time_end":114.89},{"position":42,"content":"Longer.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-14-test-2-part-1-2023-01-29-21-15-54/42.mp3","time_start":115.06,"time_end":116.18},{"position":43,"content":"It's been worse for the last couple of days,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-14-test-2-part-1-2023-01-29-21-15-54/43.mp3","time_start":116.45,"time_end":119.35},{"position":44,"content":"but it's three weeks since I first noticed it.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-14-test-2-part-1-2023-01-29-21-15-54/44.mp3","time_start":119.47,